---
// What Small Business Owners Actually Think
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="section-line bg-red-500 mb-6"></div>
    <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight mb-3">
      What Small Business Owners Actually Think
    </h2>
    <p class="font-body text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mb-10">
      This isn't our opinion. These are verified surveys of actual small business owners across America.
    </p>

    <div class="card p-6">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">"IRS should focus enforcement on wealthy individuals and corporations"</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-red-600 font-bold text-xl">91%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill bar-red" style="width: 91%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">"Small businesses are disadvantaged compared to large corporations"</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-red-600 font-bold text-xl">82%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill bar-red" style="width: 82%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">"The current tax system favors big business over small business"</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-red-600 font-bold text-xl">73%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill bar-red" style="width: 73%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">"Offshore loopholes let big businesses avoid their fair share"</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-red-600 font-bold text-xl">69%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill bar-red" style="width: 69%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="font-mono text-sm text-gray-400 mt-6">
        Small Business Majority / FACT Coalition / Small Businesses for America's Future surveys 2021-2024
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
